      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The cooks are having all kinds Of\ntrouble. Thomas Mccarthy and L..\nCurry were arrested this afternoon\nby Officer Sheehan for fighting on\nWashington street, and the same\nthree members of the cooks union\nwho created disturbance in front\nof the Ondawa Inn Wednesday were\nagain jailed this afternoon for shout\ning Unfair\" in front Of the Inn.\nAll were released on bonds."
